<br>
Looks like most of the DD poisons there are reduced.  I know Mind Melt does somethin' to the lines of 555 at level 60.  I look at a 75dd to 100 dd proc as not much.  Then again, I don't understand the system of *proc buffin'*.  Does this mean that these poison effects will kick in a random amount of times until that period of 10-15 minutes expires?  I'm really not sure.  Someone please give me a better explanation.<br>
<br>
I also remember readin' on one of the sites that Verant is very interested in expandin' the poison application.  Meanin', that Rogues would be able to apply weapons for other people.  If that happens in PoP, I see a financial horizon for Rogues in the near future.<br>
<br>
Ishkur Leroux<br>
