I'm not sure I entirely follow you here.<br>
<br>
How often: well it's the same question as &quot;how often will my weapon proc&quot;? There's probably someone who knows the numbers but I don't. It is well known that the higher your DEX the more often you proc, so a high dex will make your poison &quot;go off&quot; more often.<br>
